{"tid":2132742,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國宣布有病徵人士自我隔離日數由7日延長至10日","createTime":"2020-07-30T14:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T14:22:37.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3df6dd2326b94c9ade248a5b029c12a03b81bb7a","tid":2132742,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:22:37.000Z","msg":"英國宣布有病徵人士自我隔離日數由7日延長至10日<br />\n2020-07-30 HKT 21:08<br />\n<br />\n&quot;英國政府宣布，新型冠狀病毒檢測呈陽性，或有症狀人士的自我隔離日數，由7天延長至10天，即時生效。<br />\n<br />\n當局說，有病徵人士在出現症狀之前，以及症狀開始後的最初幾天，最具傳染性，又指目前有更多證據證明，正在康復的新型肺炎輕症患者，在發病後7至9天內感染他人，雖然可能性較低，但確實存在。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540879-20200730.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540879-20200730.htm&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDSrnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=0ee98cb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540879-20200730.htm&h=5c5c168a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540879-20200730.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">果d人自我隔離10日後就保證無傳染性？</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}